column2: New TFlex system deployed at KE012.  FW v 1.12 140211.  JAK
Recovered from KE-012.  Failed in April 2015.  System was at FLEX> prompt when connected to laptop upon recovery.  Configuration information was garbled.  No obvious cause.  JAK
Cause of issue noted 9/7/15 likely due to minor water intrusion through RF antenna port.  Sealed threads with "Blue-75."  JAK
